## Expect type

验证`true`<!-- -->类型 如果泛型参数不为 `true` 将编译不通过

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare type Expect<T extends true> = T;
```

## Example


```ts
type S = Expect<true> // 通过
type S = Expect<false> // 编译器报错
```
